msgid "Bridge"
msgstr "Droichead"

msgid "Channel Sets"
msgstr "Seiteanna Cainéal"

msgid "Data Channels"
msgstr "Cainéil Sonraí"

msgid "Define data channels over which outbound filtered packets will flow."
msgstr "Sainmhínigh cainéil sonraí ar a sreabhfaidh paicéid scagtha amach."

msgid ""
"Define filter rules to apply to outbound packets. Matching packets will flow "
"over the data channel."
msgstr ""
"Sainmhínigh rialacha scagaire le cur i bhfeidhm ar phaicéid amach. "
"Sreabhfaidh paicéid mheaitseála thar an gcainéal sonraí."

msgid "Define primary channels and their corresponding data channels."
msgstr ""
"Sainmhínigh cainéil phríomhúla agus a gcuid bealaí sonraí comhfhreagracha."

msgid "Destination port"
msgstr "Port ceann scríbe"

msgid "Dual Channel Wi-Fi AP Daemon"
msgstr "Deamhan AP Wi-Fi Dual Channel"

msgid "Dual Channel WiFi"
msgstr "Dual Channel wifi"

msgid "Enable"
msgstr "Cumasaigh"

msgid "Filter Sets"
msgstr "Tacair Scagaire"

msgid "Filters"
msgstr "Scagairí"

msgid "General"
msgstr "Ginearálta"

msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Socruithe Ginearálta"

msgid "Grant UCI access for luci-app-dcwapd"
msgstr "Deonaigh rochtain UCI do luci-app-dcwapd"

msgid "Interfaces"
msgstr "Comhéadain"

msgid "MAC Address"
msgstr "Seoladh MAC"

msgid "Packet size"
msgstr "Méid paicéad"

msgid "Protocol"
msgstr "Prótacal"

msgid "SSID"
msgstr "SSID"

msgid "Select filters to apply to matching MAC addresses."
msgstr "Roghnaigh scagairí le cur i bhfeidhm ar sheoltaí MAC a mheaitseálann."

msgid "Source IP"
msgstr "Foinse IP"

msgid "Source port"
msgstr "Source port"

msgid "Specify the temporary directory for dcwapd file storage."
msgstr "Sonraigh an t-eolaire sealadach do stóráil comhad dcwapd."

msgid "Temp Directory"
msgstr "Eolaire Temp"

msgid ""
"With %s you can use two simultaneous Wi-Fi connections to decrease wireless "
"traffic congestion and increase throughput."
msgstr ""
"Le %s is féidir leat dhá nasc Wi-Fi comhuaineach a úsáid chun brú tráchta "
"gan sreang a laghdú agus chun tréchur a mhéadú."

